FBIS4-8849 "dreeu075_i_94009" FBIS-EEU-94-075 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Gorazde Situation Worsens as Attack Continues Gorazde Situation Worsens as Attack Continues Latest Cease-Fire Ignored LD1804222494 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 2103 GMT 18 Apr 94 LD1804222494 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network English BFN [Text] Serb heavy artillery continued to pound the Moslem town of Gorazde. UN sources say tank, artillery, and sniper fire is raining down on Gorazde despite a cease-fire signed hours ago.
